response.original_title: Stan - Ensaio para Plataforma de Lançamento
response.overview: Taking advantage of the launching event as background, a young group of teenagers from São Miguel film each other dancing to Korean pop.
response.tagline: Stan Rehearsal - Ensaio para Plataforma de Lançamento is a small speculative fiction film set on the day the first rocket is launched from the (to-be built) space port in the island of Santa Maria in the Azores archipelago.
